  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You draw blood from the corpse of a creature that has been dead for no more than 24 hours and magically fashion it into a spear of frozen blood. This functions as a <em>+1 spear</em> that does cold damage instead of piercing damage. If the spear leaves your hand for more than 1 round, it melts and the spell ends.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong></em> If the spell is cast with a 4th-level spell slot, it creates a <em>+2 spear</em>. A 6th-level spell slot creates a <em>+3 spear</em>.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
